Integration of JavaFX GUI:
Explore solutions to address compatibility issues and successfully integrate JavaFX for developing a more visually appealing and interactive graphical user interface (GUI).
Enhance the user experience with modern design elements, intuitive navigation, and interactive features such as drag-and-drop functionality and real-time updates.
Mobile Application Development:
Develop a companion mobile application for iOS and Android platforms, providing customers with the convenience of placing orders, making reservations, and accessing restaurant information on-the-go.
Implement push notifications to alert users about order status updates, promotional offers, and special events, enhancing customer engagement and loyalty.
Online Ordering and Delivery Integration:
Integrate online ordering and delivery platforms such as UberEats, DoorDash, or Grubhub to expand the restaurant's reach and provide customers with convenient options for ordering food from their preferred delivery services.
Implement order tracking and delivery status updates to keep customers informed and ensure timely delivery of orders.
